reviewText:
Let me explain modules of the bomb for defuser:
Wires - Learn how to count to 6;
Button - Don't do what is written here;
Keypad - Learn some new words;
Simon Says - If you see a vowel, don't disturb expert, do it by yourself;
Who's on First - Tell the words letter by letter;
Memory - Give a pen and paper to an expert;
Morse Code - Learn Morse Code by heart;
Complicated Wires - Tell the expert to get a better scheme;
Wire sequences - Always cut the first black wire;
Maze - Learn the coordinate system;
Password - I is not a L;
Venting gas - Read the text carefully, letter by letter;
Capacitor Discharge - Lever is on the right side of the module;
Knobs - Right" means right from the "UP" word.
14 modules out of the 10"
